column5: Check out the new web page and payouts for the up and coming 2012 seasonwww.sawt.ca Thanks for looking
I haven't fished any SAWT for many years... but used to, and had a ball! Fun people! Might see if I can't do one or two this year.....
T Mac Would like to see you again this season, with the warm weather and water temps already in the 50's, fishing should be one of the best in years... Thanks G73
